their career in a particular direction,

33
00:02:09,920 --> 00:02:15,000
that is looking to help
and benefit a bunch of people working

34
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,620
towards a common goal.

35
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:20,910
If you're interested
in those things, you're going to spend

36
00:02:20,910 --> 00:02:24,780
the time to go listen to some podcasts

37
00:02:24,780 --> 00:02:28,150
outside of work,

38
00:02:28,150 --> 00:02:29,980
or during your commute.

39
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:33,160
Instead of watching
movies during your commute,

40
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:37,540
you're going to be listening to podcasts
and reading blog posts and learning more,

41
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:39,720
