56
00:03:29,870 --> 00:03:31,820
That was his question.

57
00:03:31,820 --> 00:03:33,940
And you're kind
of like, well, I don't know.

58
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:35,900
Those seem like very different things.

59
00:03:35,900 --> 00:03:37,860
